{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require training and assesment on spiking for all Personal Licence Holders.",
        "additional_details": "Introduce a simple change to training and assessment for Personal Licence Holders making it compulsory that all those involved in selling alcohol learn how to tackle spiking and identify and support victims of spiking.\r\n\r\nThis could be included in refresher courses and the cost would be minimal with huge benefits in terms of safety for customers.",
        "background": "Currently training & assessment for personal licences does not include information on spiking. We call for the Government to introduce changes to make it compulsory for all holders of Personal Licences (Alcohol) to be trained & assessed on tackling & dealing with spiking of drinks & by injection.",
